- Root cause reason: container network latency / network I/O surge (container-level network_receive_MB and packet spikes causing downstream latency and service errors)
- Evidence (concise): massive simultaneous first-crossings of P95 at 21:30 across thousands of metric series; highest per-series severities were container_network_receive_MB on adservice-1 and other backend containers; traces show elevated incoming-from-frontend durations/row_count starting at 21:30; error_logs on frontends show repeated "failed to retrieve" warnings from 21:30 onward.

